<div class="blog_post">
  <a name="python-developer"></a>
  <h2 class="blog_post_title">
  <a href="/new/2013/02/06/python-developer" rel="bookmark">
    Python Developer
  </a></h2>
  <small>February 06, 2013</small><p/>
  
  <div class="post_prose">
    
  <h2>Job Description</h2>
<p>We are seeking a dependable, enthusiastic, and detailed oriented individual to work within our systems department as a junior python programmer.</p>
<h2>Responsibilities</h2>
<ul>
<li>Developing web applications built with the Pyramid framework. These applications are driven by a PostgreSQL database.</li>
<li>Projects include collaborating with other developers using source management tools (e.g. bazaar).</li>
<li>Creating Python daemons that perform data analysis and monitoring depending on experience.</li>
</ul>
<h2>Desired Skills &amp; Experience</h2>
<ul>
<li>Fluent in Python</li>
<li>Experience working with Javascript, HTML, CSS</li>
<li>Experience creating database-driven applications</li>
<li>Good knowledge of RDBMS and SQL</li>
<li>Object-oriented programming skills</li>
</ul>
<h1>Experience in any of the following areas is an asset</h1>
<ul>
<li>Linux</li>
<li>PostgreSQL</li>
<li>Pylons / Pyramid framework</li>
<li>jQuery</li>
<li>XML</li>
</ul>
<h2>Company Description</h2>
<p>We are a facilities based telecommunications &amp; internet provider based in the Liberty Village area of the city. We have been servicing the complete telecommunication needs of downtown Toronto since 1988. We are a privately held, Canadian-owned company that owns and operates the largest private fibre-optic network throughout downtown Toronto. We primarily serve business customers, everything from small one or two person shops to fortune 500 companies.</p>
<h1>What we have to offer</h1>
<p>Competitive base salary + the opportunity to advance within the company.  A rewarding role with a chance to have a real impact on our business.  Great Benefits package including: dental, medical, vision, travel etc. Many employee incentives including: weekly lunches, discounted gym memberships, discounted TTC passes and many more.  We have a great office atmosphere that is dog-friendly.  Our office is open concept in a historical brick &amp; beam building with a fantastic view of the city. </p>

  </div>
</div>





                
